--- 
title: Shomen
summary: Standardized Ruby Documentation Format
authors: Thomas Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>
created: 2010-07-01

description:
  Shomen defines a standardized documentaiton format for Ruby
  programs which is used by other systems as a common source
  for rendering.

requires:
  - rdoc 3~
  - syckle (build)

resources:
  home: http://proutils.github.com/shomen
  work: http://github.com/proutils/shomen
  repo: git://github.com/proutils/shomen.git

